1.e4 d5
{ the idea of this repertoire in the Scandinavian is to obtain a very solid
position with black without worrying about any blitzkrieg. The position
black is aiming for is without weaknesses and has several different plans at disposal. }
2.exd5 { the only critical move. The others are much weaker } ( 2.e5 Bf5 3.d4
