2...Qxd5
{ now we have arrived at the characteristic structure of the Scandinavian.
Black's plan is as follows: when attacked the queen will go back to d8, the
Bc8 will come out to f5 or g4, the pawns go to e6 and c6, the knights to f6 and d7 and the Bf8 goes to e7, followed by castling. }
